# Place ODNI ISM specification files here:
#   CVEValues.xml     — controlled vocabulary enumerations
#   ISM-XML.xsd       — attribute structure and constraints
#   ISM-XML.sch       — Schematron cross-attribute validation rules
#   ISM-XML.rng       — RelaxNG schema
#
